shortDescription: No more tussling to get the pillows inside the cases. Our pure natural 100% cotton pillow case sets are generously sized to go over the pillows easily with some extra room should you need it. This pillowcase comes in a set of 2 and are made using luxury 400 thread count sateen weave that makes them smoother & softer - just perfect for your skin. Cotton does not trap heat, giving these white pillow cases the cooling effect & breezy breathability for a delightful sleep night after night. We adhere to the highest standard of safety and are certified STANDARD 100 by OEKO-TEX to keep our bedding free from harmful substances ensuring naturally healthy & comfortable life for you & your family.
